Package: LNMVGA
Title: Cluster microbiome / compositional data using a mixture of logistic-normal multinomial models
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Yuan", "Fang", email = "yfang8@binghamton.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8430-1238")),person("Sanjeena", "Subedi", email = "sanjeena.dang@carleton.ca", role = c("aut")))
Description: This package provides a novel mixture of logistic-normal multinomial models for clustering microbiome data, or other compositional data. Parameter estimations are accomplished using variational Gaussian approximation to lift the computational overhead.
